Privacy and User Data Policy
Data Privacy Laws
We comply with all applicable laws and regulations regarding data privacy. This
                                    includes, but is not limited to, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and
                                    the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA).
Privacy Audit
We regularly conduct privacy audits to ensure our practices and policies are in
                                    alignment with current laws and regulations. These audits also help us identify and
                                    mitigate any potential risks to user privacy.
How we handle Personal Information
We collect and store personal information with the utmost care and security. We only
                                    collect information that is necessary for providing our services and improving user
                                    experience. All personal information is stored in encrypted formats.
How we Use Personal Information
We use personal information to provide and improve our services, respond to user
                                        inquiries, and for other legitimate business purposes. We do not sell or share
                                        your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes without your
                                        consent.
Safety and Security Practices
We implement industry-standard safety and security practices to protect user
                                        data. This includes secure coding practices, regular security audits, and prompt
                                        updates and patches to address any potential vulnerabilities.
Account Deletion
If you wish to delete your account and all associated data, please send an email
                                        request to
support@stratisglobal.com
.
                                        Please note that all deletions will take place within 30 days of the request.
                                        After the deletion process is complete, you will receive an email confirmation
                                        confirming that all your user data was deleted.
We respect your decision and are committed to protecting your privacy. If you
                                        have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact our support
                                        team.